caption:
Man City’s GOAT - Kevin De Bruyne will LEAVE the club in the summer.. 🥺

2015: 🗣️ Paul Merson when Man City signed Kevin De Bruyne in 2015 for £55m: “Manchester City paying so much money for Kevin De Bruyne. It is an absolute joke. He’s going to City for about three times what Wolfsburg paid for him. Not for me.”

2025: 🗣️ Kevin De Bruyne: “These will be my final months as a Manchester City player..” 💔

He’s been at Man City since 2015. 16 trophies won and 280 goal contributions. 🪄

Kevin De Bruyne in the for Man City:
🏟️ 413 Games
🚀 106 Goals
🎯 174 Assists
✅ 108 mins per goal or assist 

Huge blow for Man City.. 💔
